@RobaloAmigo  If you switch the DNS server to a non-filtering one, the pages don't load as well?

You wrote that if you disable DNS, then ads appear, if I understand correctly filtering with filters in safari also does not work? In this case please try to disable-enable content blockers in Safari settings and restart Safari, and check for filters update.
Do not close AdGuard window 30-60 seconds.
